To build:

Prerequisites: Android NDK and SDK, Ant or Eclipse with Android plugin.

Run configure from top-level directory using the --with-android-sdk=/path/to/anrdoid-sdk option.
Compile sources (to build org.servalarch.javasock.jar)

Then excecute:

$ /path/to/android-ndk/ndk-build -j<num CPU>
$ ant debug (or build in Eclipse)
